description.narrative: To develop trade along Corridor Vc by improving the capacity, efficiency and quality of services on the southern end of Corridor Vc with particular focus on the port of Ploce and on coordination aspects among all corridor participants. Theproject seeks to achieve this objective through: (i) increased throughput capacity of the port and railway infrastructure (ii) efficient operation of the corridor including the Port of Ploce; (iii) high quality of services; (iv) competitivealternative to other corridors; and, (v) increased private sector involvement to address these priorities, reduce commercial risks and secure financing for port cargo handling equipment.
